1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Midnight — that's when they come out to feed.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:11,000
Mmm, this cat meat is so tender.

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Finish up. We've got "rent" to collect in the east court — Lady Zhang's turn this month.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,000
"Rent"? They collect lives like rent.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Well, if it isn't Consort Lin. Your blood smells far sweeter than hers.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:23,000
Wait... she smells like a demon. A strong one.

7
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:25,000
A washed-up concubine? A demon? Please.

8
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:31,000
This... this is impossible...

9
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:34,000
Who's first? Or all at once?

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Too slow.

11
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,000
3 minor demons slain. EXP +30. Demon blood refined — 80/100.

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Still 20 short...

13
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:51,000
I know you're down there. Come up. Let's talk.

14
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:56,000
A discarded concubine with ancient demon blood... and she comes alone? Bold.

15
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Century-old serpent demon. Silver Rank, early stage. Threat: high.

16
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Devour you, and I might become a dragon. A banquet, two nights from now. Will you come?

17
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,500
I'll come.

18
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:06,500
See you then, Consort Lin.

19
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:09,500
A trap dinner? I'll show this snake who the real hunter is.
